    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After you deploy your token contract, the deployer is the `owner`. Only the owner is allowed to mint tokens, so to use a `MintableCrowdsale`, the crowdsale must be the owner. You can change the owner of the token by doing `token.transferOwnership(crowdsaleAddress)`.\r\n\r\nIf you are using truffle to deploy, you can make this transaction part of your deploy script",
