    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The old version of OpenZeppelin's crowdsale created the token as part of the crowdsale, but there were a few issues with it, mainly inflexibility and the increased deployment size.\r\n\r\nYou can create a `Factory` contract that \r\n- deploys the token with your arguments\r\n- deploys the crowdsale with your arguments\r\n- transfers the ownership of the token to the crowdsale\r\n\r\nall in one transaction if you'd like",
